overview:
The Law Offices Scott Gottlieb & Associates, LLP handle all type of personal injury and medical malpractice cases. We strive to provide excellent service and strong representation to each of our clients.

Our firm is comprised of experienced lawyers, legal assistants, medical assistants, and support staff. We have access to an extensive network of professionals including accident reconstruction experts, investigators, photographers, and economists. Our goal is to provide quality legal service to our clients and to help ensure they receive a fair compensation for their damages.
